06:45.000 --> 06:48.000
This is not the case in the United States and Canada.

06:48.000 --> 06:51.000
The U.S. Department of State does not have a law department.

06:51.000 --> 06:54.000
You have to graduate from the Department of State

06:54.000 --> 06:57.000
