13:07.000 --> 13:09.000
So in most cases,

13:09.000 --> 13:11.000
in general, in Taiwan or Japan,

13:11.000 --> 13:13.000
if you have been a lawyer for three or five years

13:13.000 --> 13:14.000
and you think you need to retire,

13:14.000 --> 13:15.000
you can go to the U.S.

13:15.000 --> 13:18.000
