Chinese people do not want to

48:26.000 --> 48:28.000
get along with U.S. citizens,

48:28.000 --> 48:30.000
which will worsen Sino-U.S. relations

48:30.000 --> 48:32.000
and damage U.S. business interests in China.

48:32.000 --> 48:34.000
My question is

48:34.000 --> 48:36.000
if foreign law is really better,

48:36.000 --> 48:38.000
how does it actually work?

