53:32.000 --> 53:34.000
Because they thought

53:34.000 --> 53:36.000
it was different.

53:36.000 --> 53:38.000
At first, they thought

53:38.000 --> 53:40.000
it was the same thing.

53:40.000 --> 53:42.000
Their opposition was

53:42.000 --> 53:44.000
when they found

