We would say that

54:06.000 --> 54:08.000
we thought that the subjective

54:08.000 --> 54:10.000
will of the activists

54:10.000 --> 54:12.000
at that time

54:12.000 --> 54:14.000
mixed it with

54:14.000 --> 54:16.000
legal pluralism.

